144
00:17:31.619 --> 00:17:34.246
Pluto... Gerçek ismi Lenny Franklin.

145
00:17:34.997 --> 00:17:37.041
Aslen Şikago'lu.

146
00:17:37.208 --> 00:17:40.336
Altı yıl önce, 
Ray'le birlikte...

147
00:17:40.544 --> 00:17:43.464
